# OAuth apps.
# GitHub OAuth Apps have a single callback URL, so create dev/prod apps:
#   tokenmasala-dev -> http://api.tokenmasala.localhost:8788/auth/github/callback
#   tokenmasala     -> https://api.tokenmasala.xyz/auth/github/callback
# Google Web OAuth clients should include:
#   http://api.tokenmasala.localhost:8788/auth/google/callback
#   https://api.tokenmasala.xyz/auth/google/callback
# This file (.env) holds DEV pairs and only feeds `bun run dev`.
# Deploys load .env.production (prod pairs) via --env-file;
# CI deploys on main pushes use repo secrets instead.
GITHUB_CLIENT_ID=
GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET=
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=
